timeline.bodyText:
Rather than using negation, it might be a touch clearer here to add a method hasExplicitUpperBound() to BoundType.  Then this test can be
if (insideBoundType.hasExplicitUpperBound() && outside.hasExplicitUpperBound())
which I think is more readable.

